Chole Dancer / Crown of Thorns
By Mother Love Bone, covered by Pearl Jam on a regular basis

CHLOE DANCER

Piano intro/verse, transcribed for guitar, standard tuning
(NB: if the big reach back to 2 on the low E string is too much, you can capo fret 2 but 
then remove the capo when you transition to Crown of Thorns; ALTERNATELY play this 
intro transposed down two frets so you can use the open E string, but then the transition to Crown of Thorns
is more dissonant since you still need to get to fret 5 base for those chords)

