Solo
Rhythm:
E5        CM7 E5        CM7 E5
E5 slide Em7 slide E5

Key:
() - harmonic
r - let ring
b – bend
u – unbend
b/u – bend and unbend repeatedly
p – pull off
h – hammer on
s – slide
t – trill (hammer on pull off quickly)


